description: Erection of a 5 storey building and basement mixed use scheme comprising of B1 floor space (1842m2), cafe (A3) (191m2), nursery (D1) (304m2), 71 residential units (17 x 3 bed, 30 x 2 bed, 24 x 1 bed) together with balconies and basement parking for 38 cars, 60 bicycles and altered vehicle access to Orsman Road.
